Class RasterBase

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.gvsig.raster.cache.buffer.RasterBase
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    PxTile

    public abstract class RasterBase
extends Object
    Base class for raster elements. This class contains methos for reading width, height, number of bands and other raster parameters
